# Vue 3 + Typescript + Vite 滑块验证码

This repository rewrite from [vue-monoplasty-slide-verify](https://github.com/monoplasty/vue-monoplasty-slide-verify), and the main function remain the same, but just changed from vue2 to vue3. Meanwhile ,the front-end and backend interactive verification scheme is added.

该包主要是将 [vue-monoplasty-slide-verify](https://github.com/monoplasty/vue-monoplasty-slide-verify)的vue2版本改为了vue3+typescript版本，主功能未曾改变，但为了该包更具验证码的验证特性，我增加了前后端交互认证方案。

# Install 安装

```
npm i dawn-vue3-slide-verify
```

# Use 使用

```
// 1. code added in main.ts
// 1. 在main.ts中增加代码

import SlideVerify from 'dawn-vue3-slide-verify'
import 'dawn-vue3-slide-verify/dist/style.css'

createApp(App).use(SlideVerify).mount('#app')
```

```
// 2. for interactive verification both in front-end and backend, package a component again & please pay attention to the notes
// 2. 为了让前后端联合做验证，我在前端业务中又写了一个公共的引用组件：src/components/SlideVerifyShow.vue，代码如下：
// 注意代码中的注释内容

<template>
  <slide-verify
    v-if="visible"
    :blockPosition="blockPosition"
    :imgs="imgList"
    @success="onSuccess"
  />
</template>
<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent, reactive, toRefs, onMounted } from "vue";
import { getVerify } from "@/apis/common.ts";

export default defineComponent({
  emits: ["success"],
  setup(props, { emit }) {
    const data = reactive({
      visible: <boolean>false,
      blockPosition: <object>{
        blockX: <number>0,
        blockY: <number>0,
      },
      imgList: <string[]>[],
    });

    const initImgs = () => {
      interface ImgFiles {
        [key: string]: any;
      }

      const files: ImgFiles = import.meta.globEager(
        "/src/assets/slideverify-images/*.jpg" // 我在这里引用的是我的静态资源列表，大家可以自行放置 // here, add image list by yourself with another ways
      );
      const images: string[] = [];

      for (const key in files) {
        if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(files, key)) {
          images.push((<ImgFiles>files)[key].default);
        }
      }

      data.imgList = images;
    };

    onMounted(async () => {
      if (data.imgList.length === 0) {
        initImgs();
      }

      let result = await getVerify();
      if (result.success) {
        data.blockPosition.blockX = result.blockX;
        data.blockPosition.blockY = result.blockY;
        data.visible = true;
      }
    });

    const onSuccess = (params) => {
      console.log(params); // {timestamp: 1284, left: 149, accuracy: 5}
      emit("success", params); // 当成功后，在业务中将组件反馈出来的数据连同“登录或发送短信等业务数据”发送到后端去验证验证码位置是否准确 // when success, combine the 'params' with the business data & send them to backend together
    };

    const dataAsRefs = toRefs(data);
    return { ...dataAsRefs, onSuccess };
  },
});
</script>

```

```
// 2.1. getVerify函数是用来获取后端接口中传递过来的滑块位置的，我现在是简单写了一下，大家可以根据自己的request方法做API封装 // this is the 'getVerify()', just for test

export const getVerify = () => {
  return Promise.resolve({ success:true,blockX: 150, blockY: 50 })
}

```

```
// 3. 后端代码 - 生成位置函数（PHP版） // backend codes with php - generate verify info
// L:block真实长度  w:图片长度 h:图片高度 r:block半径
// L: block real length; w: the image width; h: the image height; r: block radius
// L = block.l + block.r * 2 + 3
public function info(Request $request, array $params, string $type = self::TYPE_LOGIN): array
{
    // 3.1产生位置信息 - generate 
    $blockX = $this->getRandomNumberByRange($params['L'] + 10, $params['w'] - ($params['L'] + 10));
    $blockY = $this->getRandomNumberByRange($params['r'] * 2 + 10, $params['h'] - ($params['L'] + 10));

    // 3.2这是symfony中的session设置方式，如果不用symfony的，则自行将信息设置到session中 - put infos to session
    $request->getSession()->set($type.':verify:blockX', $blockX);
    $request->getSession()->set($type.':verify:blockY', $blockY);

    return ['blockX' => $blockX, 'blockY' => $blockY];
}

protected function getRandomNumberByRange(int $end, int $start): int
{
    return (int) round(random_int(1, 100) / 100 * ($end - $start) + $start);
}

```

```
// 4. 后端代码 - 验证滑块验证码位置是否正确（PHP版）// backend codes with php - check
public function check(Request $request, array $params, string $type = self::TYPE_LOGIN): bool
    {
        if (!$request->getSession()->has($type.':verify:blockX')) {
            return false;
        }

        // 从session中获取到位置信息 - get infos from session
        $blockX = $request->getSession()->get($type.':verify:blockX');
        $accuracy = sprintf('%.2f', abs($params['left'] - $blockX));
        $params['accuracy'] = sprintf('%.2f', $params['accuracy']);

        // 比较位置，是否在可接受范围内 - check the accuracy
        if (bccomp($accuracy, $params['accuracy'], 2) <= 0) {
            $request->getSession()->remove($type.':verify:blockX');
            $request->getSession()->remove($type.':verify:blockY');

            return true;
        }

        $request->getSession()->remove($type.':verify:blockX');
        $request->getSession()->remove($type.':verify:blockY');

        return false;
    }
```

`
5.前后端验证的流程是：前端从后端info()获取滑块验证码位置 -> 前端滑块验证码验证通过后，将组件中的数据连同业务数据传递给后端 -> 后端在处理业务之前先拿取到验证码信息去check()函数中验证
`

# 参数
name |类型 |  备注 |  默认值  
-|-|-|-
l | Number |block length | 5 |
r | Number |block radius | 10 |
w | Number |canvas width | 310 |
h | Number |canvas height | 155 |
sliderText |String  |slider bottom text | 向右滑动 |
accuracy | Number  |check accuracy | 5 |
show | Boolean  | if show this component | true |
imgs | Array  | imgs list, if length = 0, get the component default images | [] |
blockPosition | Object  | the int position of block, if unset, generate them by Math.rand() | {blockX:0,blockY:0} |
